com.aionemu.commons.configuration
Annotation Type Property

@Documented
@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Property

This annotation is used to mark field that should be processed by ConfigurableProcessor

This annotation is Documented, all definitions with it will appear in javadoc

Required Element Summary
 java.lang.String key
          Property name in configuration
 
Optional Element Summary
 java.lang.String defaultValue
          Represents default value that will be parsed if key not found.
 java.lang.Class<? extends PropertyTransformer> propertyTransformer
          PropertyTransformer to use.
 

Element Detail

key

public abstract java.lang.String key
Property name in configuration

Returns:
name of the property that will be used

propertyTransformer

public abstract java.lang.Class<? extends PropertyTransformer> propertyTransformer
PropertyTransformer to use.
List of automaticly transformed types:
  • Boolean and boolean by BooleanTransformer
  • Byte and byte by ByteTransformer
  • Character and char by CharTransformer
  • Short and short by ShortTransformer
  • Integer and int by IntegerTransformer
  • Float and float by FloatTransformer
  • Long and long by LongTransformer
  • Double and double by DoubleTransformer
  • String by StringTransformer
  • Enum and enum by EnumTransformer
  • File by FileTransformer
  • InetSocketAddress by InetSocketAddressTransformer
  • Pattern by PatternTransformer

If your value is one of this types - just leave this field empty

Returns:
returns class that will be used to transform value
Default:
com.aionemu.commons.configuration.PropertyTransformer.class

defaultValue

public abstract java.lang.String defaultValue
Represents default value that will be parsed if key not found. If this key equals(default) DEFAULT_VALUE init value of the object won't be overriden

Returns:
default value of the property
Default:
"DO_NOT_OVERWRITE_INITIALIAZION_VALUE"
